        <content type="html" xml:base="https://sacanthias.github.io/projects/starlit/">&lt;p&gt;Starlit Wanderer was a personal project developed for the Granola.gg 2024 Game Jam, based on the theme word &#x27;nostalgia.&#x27;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this 48-hour game jam, I was responsible for asset production, which included in-game sprites and resources, cutscenes, and background patterns. All assets were made in Aseprite&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
